{"tid":1029342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍人請注意，有針筒狂徒出沒","createTime":"2019-02-20T07:26:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T13:17:35.000Z","uid":66260,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"35b0654ead4f27b74fb5029d87a44a46cc607533","tid":1029342,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:26:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1965349193577706&amp;id=327046987407943\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D1965349193577706%26id%3D327046987407943&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n8xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=160f2b29\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=1965349193577706&amp;id=327046987407943</a><br />\n<br />\n天水圍人請注意<br />\n事情發生係2月19號 晚上11點左右<br />\n地點係銀座空地附近<br />\n啱啱同朋友食完許留山 向住大噴水池嗰邊走<br />\n行到兩個商場中間嗰個位 突然有個陌生男人迎面撞到我朋友(女仔)<br />\n我朋友即刻嗌左聲 同停左係到望住我地<br />\n個男人講聲對唔住就繼續行<br />\n當時後面有個家庭經過睇到件事<br />\n個爸爸指住個男人同我地講話佢係特登<br />\n嗰時我地仲以為朋友比人非禮 所以就大喝左佢一聲問佢做咩<br />\n但佢嗰時已經走遠左 離遠講多句唔好意思就加快走左<br />\n嗰時大家都未反應過黎 唔知應該點處理 所以關心下朋友點樣<br />\n嗰刻先知原來個男人唔係非禮佢 而係有啲尖野拮到佢手臂<br />\n我朋友已經着左長袖衫加外套 但都穿透哂啲衫拮到佢<br />\n拉開隻袖見到有個好細既小血洞傷口<br />\n由於好擔心唔知比咩拮到 最後都係去醫院睇睇先<br />\n大家出街都要多啲留意身邊既人！<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n更新<br />\n1. 朋友需要三個月後再去驗血<br />\n2. 睇完醫生報埋警<br />\n3. 該名男子應該係20-30歲既年青人<br />\n身高估計170左右<br />\n着外套無戴眼鏡揹書包<br />\n手上揸住一舊疑似機頂盒物體<br />\n由於事發時銀座已經無乜燈<br />\n加上發生太快太突然 大家後尾講返都對佢衣着等等既野好模糊<br />\n<br />\n4. 醫生話好小機會有d咩病 但之後要再驗多幾次<br />\n5. 報左警 落左口供&amp;去銀座案件重演 CID會查<br />\n6. 有谷友睇完post pm我 同我講琴晚10:45係天頌苑見過類似男人 希望警方會再查"},{"pid":"13f57faa88d454ff0a85aecc35790c5e15653252","tid":1029342,"uid":170249,"like":17,"dislike":4,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:27:55.000Z","msg":"牛屎地方既村民真係恐怖<br />\n<br />\n睇黎今晚我騎牛返屋企要更加小心"},{"pid":"8cb025cd29e09a9a29ff250eb81b989cd618c76c","tid":1029342,"uid":124491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:28:42.000Z","msg":"愛滋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b25002f367a2b78c374f05b00dcc413d118be80d","tid":1029342,"uid":222918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"屌 我所有特徵中哂，但我冇咁做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1a36d7efcfa100ca7e01475b942c4d529d7ece8","tid":1029342,"uid":145589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:31:13.000Z","msg":"呢d地方真係好多痴線佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff81d3f3e6df744abce0e264b313d38fb552fa84","tid":1029342,"uid":86040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25002f367a2b78c374f05b00dcc413d118be80d","tid":1029342,"uid":222918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"屌 我所有特徵中哂，但我冇咁做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:31:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"064037e09c79f9065e99e478c7cdd36f11017ba7","tid":1029342,"uid":66260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b25002f367a2b78c374f05b00dcc413d118be80d","tid":1029342,"uid":222918,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T07:29:13.000Z","msg":"屌 我所有特徵中哂，但我冇咁做過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T08:21:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /